      "writtenOn": "2017-12-04T19:58:07Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "No it\u0027s moreso that WriterGenerator is call for from multiple threads, so WriterGenerator captures some mutable state and accesses it, without a lock or some kind of synchronization you could risk corrupting state.",
      "parentUuid": "9d312594_daa9bbcd",
      "revId": "202af8115b472ffaa293a9c0ac0f42a4fad8fa2e",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
